Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.27,0:00:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, your journey's proven to be quite a long one.{wow, no "welcome to the velvet room"}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.61,0:00:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be able to resolve your ordeal in time?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.20,0:00:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't much time left.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.62,0:00:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be able to reach out to the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.46,0:00:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could call this the {\i1}final{\i0} moment of truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.92,0:00:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{OP}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.94,0:00:52.65,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Hide and seek it wants to play again
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.65,0:00:55.45,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,100)}Like a detective, I won't let it get away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.45,0:00:58.16,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}It's constantly costuming with loads of fake
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.24,0:01:00.49,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,100)}I will strip search if I have to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.49,0:01:03.62,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Though I'm not afraid to know it, don't know how {No I'm not afraid to know it no, no, no}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.62,0:01:05.79,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,100)} I am so determined
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.79,0:01:14.09,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}To chase after what's hidden and seize this day, this moment
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.68,0:01:19.60,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)\an1}WANNA KNOW
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.64,0:01:20.30,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Enter key to accelerate {And I keep accelerate}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.60,0:01:23.31,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)\an1}WANNA GO
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.06,0:01:24.02,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Ignition turned on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.02,0:01:27.73,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}It's about that time to drive to truth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.73,0:01:30.61,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,100)\an1}WANNA SEIZE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.48,0:01:31.27,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Stranger than in movies
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.61,0:01:33.99,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(100,100)\an1}WANNA SEIZE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.94,0:01:34.11,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Ignorance is not bliss
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.11,0:01:36.82,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}They say that truth will out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.49,0:01:39.57,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)} Can't keep on hiding
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.57,0:01:41.87,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}There's no turning back now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.87,0:01:43.33,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)} I'm gonna go on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.33,0:01:47.08,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}I'm gonna go get what I want
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.51,0:02:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you to a place...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.81,0:02:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where you can be at peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.82,0:02:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did the best I could to look into it,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.24,0:02:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but there's nothing that would indicate the sender's identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.12,0:02:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.50,0:02:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.04,0:02:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since he personally left it in your mailbox,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.55,0:02:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's highly likely that the culprit is closer to us than we think.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.88,0:02:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should probably look for clues around that area.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.93,0:02:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you're like a regular Sherlock Holmes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.64,0:02:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naoto, you're like a totally different person when you talk about the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.39,0:02:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Y-You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.56,0:02:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares?! That's not what's important!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.07,0:02:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A dangerous criminal found out where he lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.40,0:03:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows what'll happen if we don't do something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.57,0:03:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.78,0:03:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is disconcerting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.20,0:03:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Disconcerting?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.37,0:03:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're absolutely right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.46,0:03:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful, Yu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.25,0:03:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give us a call if anything happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.83,0:03:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.01,0:03:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may be looking at this differently than everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.60,0:03:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.14,0:03:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About what Tatsumi said earlier... He was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.52,0:03:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Considering the situation, I should be concerned for your safety first and foremost.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.73,0:03:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.61,0:03:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I probably have no right to be your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.86,0:03:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not when I hold solving the case as my top priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.74,0:03:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.58,0:03:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.34,0:04:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.59,0:04:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.01,0:04:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Now for our next story.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.31,0:04:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}There's been much conjecture on the origin of the fog,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.77,0:04:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}and some are concerned about its effects on the human body.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.69,0:04:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you lost your appetite?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}In response, Mr. Kozai of the Environmental Concern Society
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.74,0:04:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-uh. I'm okay.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:23.28,0:04:26.82,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5\fs48\pos(654,563)\c&HF1F1E9&}Investigation Held to Identify the "Mysterious Fog" in Inaba
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.28,0:04:26.82,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1a&H00&\bord4\blur0\fs48\pos(654,563)\c&H613D2F&\3c&H613D2F&}Investigation Held to Identify the "Mysterious Fog" in Inaba
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.41,0:04:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}visited a local elementary school to investigate the effects of the fog.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.12,0:04:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he came to my school!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.75,0:04:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.79,0:04:39.34,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.8\fscx96\fs40\pos(641,573)\c&HE9EFEB&}What are the facts? An interview with Mr. Kozai of the Environmental Concern Society
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.79,0:04:39.34,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1a&HFF&\bord4\fscx96\fs40\pos(641,573)\c&HE9EFEB&\3c&H8F7355&}What are the facts? An interview with Mr. Kozai of the Environmental Concern Society
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.08,0:04:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Today, I spoke with a young student who spoke her own mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.21,0:04:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}free from the influence of those around her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.84,0:04:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}It was an attitude and example that we as adults can learn from.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.71,0:04:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My head hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.93,0:04:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're burning up!{ufufufufu}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.43,0:04:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because it was cold today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.43,0:04:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I hate the cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.81,0:04:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be spring soon enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.60,0:04:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it'll warm right up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But aren't you leaving in the spring?{;_;}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.57,0:05:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.74,0:05:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to make snowmen with you when it snows!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.71,0:05:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Let's make a big one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.96,0:05:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.92,0:05:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.55,0:05:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.63,0:05:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.59,0:05:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, let's play a whole lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.70,0:05:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.04,0:05:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible to tell who it was based off that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.54,0:06:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be sure to watch the Midnight Channel tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.59,0:06:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.84,0:06:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.59,0:06:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, Big Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.68,0:06:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like your fever's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.77,0:06:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's still cold out,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.39,0:06:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so you should go to bed early tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.10,0:06:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aww! But I wanna watch TV!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.86,0:06:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.94,0:06:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to hurry and get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.74,0:06:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.28,0:06:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. So you have a space heater!{kotatsu lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.20,0:06:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy said we could use it if we got cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.45,0:06:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.00,0:06:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What gives?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.00,0:06:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it broken?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.13,0:06:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.92,0:06:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go buy a new one later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.92,0:06:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.22,0:06:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we get it at Junes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.76,0:06:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.89,0:06:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can get Yosuke to cut us a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.80,0:06:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay, I love Junes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.47,0:06:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Daddy's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.77,0:07:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome ho—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.94,0:07:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was in the mailbox.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.11,0:07:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.36,0:07:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks.
