Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.67,0:07:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to hear what this is all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.45,0:07:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So you don't want to discuss this here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.83,0:07:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're heading out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.42,0:07:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy! Big Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.42,0:07:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. We're just going out to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.34,0:07:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.47,0:07:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.60,0:08:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yu, I think of you as a member of the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.11,0:08:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's precisely why I should've done this sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.15,0:08:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uncle...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.32,0:08:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to tell me everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.57,0:08:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From what you're involved in to how you got involved. Everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.83,0:08:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also think of you as family.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.92,0:08:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.42,0:08:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.42,0:08:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.67,0:08:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.34,0:08:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.18,0:08:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,been involved in the serial murder case.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.43,0:08:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We rescue the people who get kidnapped...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.69,0:08:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by going inside the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.36,0:08:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inside the TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.40,0:08:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are enemies called "Shadows," which we fight using Personas—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.28,0:09:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It hasn't been long enough for you to trust me like your old man,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.95,0:09:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I hoped you'd open up to me a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.87,0:09:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.67,0:09:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uncle, please believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.34,0:09:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Send this to the lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.00,0:09:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.51,0:09:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.13,0:09:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay here for the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.56,0:09:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.14,0:09:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dojima's just worried about you is all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.52,0:09:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was probably just tough love.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.90,0:09:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll be just outside this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.49,0:09:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call if you need anything, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.12,0:09:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, why do I have to pitch in with stock duty?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.12,0:09:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The 8 o'clock clearance sale has begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.13,0:09:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because I'm not working hard enough! There's no getting around it!{lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.92,0:10:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really shouldn't have gotten this for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.59,0:10:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotten what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.76,0:10:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.43,0:10:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang onto it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.14,0:10:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your own cell. We'd get worried if we couldn't reach you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.27,0:10:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you, Yosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.19,0:10:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You use it by... Scrap that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.44,0:10:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just show you how I use mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.44,0:10:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}At Junes, every day is Customer Appreciation Day!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.99,0:10:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll give Yu a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.99,0:10:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Every day's great at your Junes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.75,0:10:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try his home phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.75,0:10:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.71,0:10:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Nanako? Is Yu around?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.05,0:10:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.42,0:10:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}If it's Nana, give the phone to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.05,0:10:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not home. He got a weird letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.05,0:10:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy got mad when he saw it and took him to the police station.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.68,0:10:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The police station?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.93,0:10:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Gimme the phone! Gimme the phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.35,0:10:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's at the door. I gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.81,0:10:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Nana, it's your bear-y good friend Teddie!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.64,0:10:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, sorry to bother you. See ya later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.94,0:10:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Lemme talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.69,0:10:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! You hung up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.23,0:11:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A letter? It couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.83,0:11:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanako?!
