Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.35,0:11:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,717)}How could it be her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.89,0:11:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,717)}She hasn't been on TV!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.64,0:11:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,717)}No, she {\i1}was{\i0} on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.64,0:11:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,717)}Nanako wasn't seen, but she was heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.77,0:11:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,717)}Huh? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.23,0:11:42.61,Default,,0100,0100,0000,,{\pos(640,717)}Do you remember the politician who visited a local school
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.61,0:11:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,717)}and made the news several times?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.78,0:11:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,717)}In those interviews,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.91,0:11:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,717)}he always quoted a particular student he spoke with.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.53,0:11:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,717)}Oh yeah, I remember watching that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.00,0:11:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,717)}The child became well-known,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.62,0:11:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,717)}while remaining anonymous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.79,0:11:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,717)}That girl was Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.75,0:11:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,717)}No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.96,0:11:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,717)}A reporter who took interest in this
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.84,0:12:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,released her photo and interview using her real name in today's evening paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.51,0:12:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even before that, this is a small rural town.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.84,0:12:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her identity must've been circulating for quite some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.47,0:12:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.81,0:12:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should've realized it much sooner!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.14,0:12:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was so hung up on the idea of people who were "shown" on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.48,0:12:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are we gonna do? Nanako's home alone right now, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.28,0:12:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on my way there as we speak to check on her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.53,0:12:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me out, Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.91,0:12:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.41,0:12:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Adachi, open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.00,0:12:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.92,0:12:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanako... Nanako's in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.96,0:12:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.47,0:12:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't open that door!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.01,0:12:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Fuck off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.97,0:12:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Rawr!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.01,0:12:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to talk to Yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.51,0:12:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hey, stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.18,0:12:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.47,0:12:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yosuke?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.10,0:12:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.81,0:13:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanako...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.77,0:13:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanako's missing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.40,0:13:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.61,0:13:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Shirogane.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.16,0:13:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirogane, you there? What the hell's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.58,0:13:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just at your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.66,0:13:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The front door was open, and there was no one inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.96,0:13:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid that Nanako's been kidnapped by the serial killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.47,0:13:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dojima, surely you must've known.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.01,0:13:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The case isn't over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.52,0:13:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The number you have dialed is unavailable right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.52,0:13:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you'd like, you may leave a mess—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.90,0:13:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.44,0:13:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! Why Nanako?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.28,0:13:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uncle...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.03,0:13:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.95,0:13:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go look for my daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.87,0:13:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But do you even have any ideas or leads on who took her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.66,0:14:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make a checkpoint by the highway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.33,0:14:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That won't help.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.42,0:14:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.59,0:14:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.71,0:14:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.50,0:14:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.92,0:14:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.34,0:14:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know I can't let you go! Yu, be reasonable!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.68,0:14:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut your fuckin' mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.60,0:14:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.31,0:14:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Nana's in a bear-y dangerous situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.02,0:14:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta go save her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.43,0:14:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Nana's in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.68,0:14:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll you do if something happens to her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.10,0:14:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gonna take responsibility if something happens to Nanako?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.65,0:14:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to call back-up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.73,0:14:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Narukami!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.90,0:14:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're multiplying!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.69,0:14:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Narukami!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.94,0:14:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.24,0:14:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, did they lock you in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.07,0:14:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Adachi, please release him and the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.04,0:14:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you know I can't do—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.45,0:14:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move aside, Naoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.46,0:14:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know how you feel,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.54,0:14:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but if you don't tell me what's going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.29,0:14:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's really nothing I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.30,0:14:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, so you agree to release them once we explain the situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.47,0:14:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, that's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.97,0:14:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naoto, we don't have time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.60,0:15:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.52,0:15:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all take a moment to stop and sort out the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.85,0:15:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps this will help Adachi understand as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.44,0:15:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.82,0:15:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Narukami,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.65,0:15:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if we run out blindly, we'll have no idea where to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.28,0:15:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no doubt in my mind that this is a kidnapping by the same culprit who was behind the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.37,0:15:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, consider that the front door at Nanako's house was open.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.50,0:15:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I examined it and found no trace that entry had been forced.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.67,0:15:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Nanako opened the door herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.17,0:15:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The culprit didn't sneak in. He came boldly up to the front door and rung the doorbell.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.22,0:15:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like how it was for all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.93,0:15:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... "For all of us"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.01,0:15:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the circumstances are different for her compared to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.89,0:15:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember what Nanako said when we were at the hot springs?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.90,0:15:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(275,275}"I always do what my dad tells me, like not opening the door for strangers!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.19,0:15:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So is the killer someone Nanako knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.70,0:15:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Huh? What? How'd you figure that out?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.45,0:15:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like we're closing in on who it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.95,0:15:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we need more info.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.12,0:16:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let us change our perspective slightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.62,0:16:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His quick work is what stood out to me when he caught me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.96,0:16:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said he threw you in immediately after being kidnapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.71,0:16:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would go as far as to say that it took place in front of their houses.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.92,0:16:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning he had a TV out front.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.39,0:16:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The culprit is taking a TV with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.01,0:16:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.31,0:16:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, it's highly likely that he drives to the scene of the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.98,0:16:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it would take a car large enough to hold a fairly big TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.06,0:16:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A large car...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.90,0:16:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, no unusual vehicles have been sighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.90,0:16:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd expect someone to notice since most of the victims vanished during the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.95,0:16:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's someone Nanako knows who has a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.95,0:16:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's a car that can't be seen?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.00,0:16:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's one you wouldn't notice even if you saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.84,0:16:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A delivery truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.10,0:17:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.72,0:17:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A delivery came! It was a delivery truck!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.93,0:17:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one looks twice at a delivery truck, no matter where it's parked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.90,0:17:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it were a local company, it'd be the same deliveryman every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.69,0:17:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that explains it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.28,0:17:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Adachi, is there anyone who fits this profile?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.03,0:17:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I don't really know.{adachi, the misterx of policemen}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.20,0:17:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you're not too far off base.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.12,0:17:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dojima put this stuff together to reinvestigate the first case,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.13,0:17:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and one of the suspects for Ms. Yamano's murder was a delivery man.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.46,0:17:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think he was a city council secretary before becoming a delivery man.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.43,0:17:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A secretary? That's Namatame Taro.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.18,0:17:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guy who had the affair with Ms. Yamano?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.39,0:17:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Adachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.23,0:17:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.32,0:18:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's been a break in the case, I'd better hurry to the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.83,0:18:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just have to hope nothing happens here while I'm gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.50,0:18:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.80,0:18:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there, Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.22,0:18:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dojima, where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.34,0:18:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On a road by the highway! If this isn't urgent—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.81,0:18:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The perp! I know who the culprit is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.18,0:18:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just as you suspected!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.73,0:18:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the delivery man!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.65,0:18:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Namatame!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.23,0:18:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Namatame Taro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.20,0:18:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's leave Namatame's car to Dojima and Adachi for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.87,0:18:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take us to Junes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.87,0:18:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanako...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.38,0:19:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's headed for the highway via the Inaba Shopping District's main street!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.09,0:19:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not letting you get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.19,0:19:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dojima!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.84,0:19:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.06,0:19:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dojima, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.93,0:19:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.85,0:19:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Where's Nanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.65,0:19:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? We need an ambulance, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.44,0:20:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.82,0:20:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Nanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.91,0:20:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Namatame?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.95,0:20:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.70,0:20:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.04,0:20:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't! We have to preserve the crime scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.29,0:20:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then leave that to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.21,0:20:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanamura, pay him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.21,0:20:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dude! I swear, I'm not your sugar daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.80,0:20:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The door's open.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.80,0:20:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.89,0:20:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.39,0:20:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.06,0:20:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There really is a TV in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.06,0:20:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Narukami?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.48,0:20:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.90,0:20:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go rescue Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.48,0:20:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if you end up somewhere dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.49,0:20:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to try!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.49,0:20:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{Senpai}Stop it! If we fail, who's going to save Nanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.41,0:20:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This diary...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.00,0:20:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}They're doing their own thing again...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.46,0:20:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It probably belonged to Namatame.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.79,0:21:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I discovered the existence of a new world."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.46,0:21:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Thus, I must save people."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.30,0:21:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Save"?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.72,0:21:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hell's he mean by that?
