Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.81,0:21:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a list of the victims' home addresses!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.85,0:21:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamano Mayumi, Konishi Saki,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.35,0:21:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amagi Yukiko, Tatsumi Kanji, Kujikawa Rise...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.15,0:21:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the victims who survived and were never released to the public are written here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.90,0:21:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I note that Mr. Morooka's address is absent from the list.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.11,0:21:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow... Then that settles it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.45,0:21:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The last date is today's.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.62,0:21:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I can't believe such a small child appeared on it."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.79,0:21:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I must save this child, no matter what."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.83,0:21:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that... about Nanako?!
