Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.56,0:22:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.61,0:22:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yu...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.03,0:22:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanako...
